    <data key="d0">Glidewell Laboratories IoT Dental Restoration Monitoring</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5RsZJ-1_sn4</data>
    <data key="d2">Glidewell Laboratories scales from 3,400 to over 4,000 unique dental restorations per day. The architecture ingests 1 million IoT messages per day, calculates real-time operational statistics, and initiates automated machine recalibration (self-healing) or alerts human operators based on detected telemetry anomalies.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
